{"tid":102432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肖建華在一群女保鏢陪同下被便衣公安帶走","createTime":"2017-01-31T15:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T03:20:51.000Z","uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae127cdd1865b4fdb0dcce6dde9e2c21a16b5e3e","tid":102432,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》引述知情人士指肖與其2名保安是於年三十（27日）凌約晨1時，被「5至6名公安便衣」從四季酒店的服務式住所帶走。報道指酒店向香港警察提供閉路電視片段，<span style=\"color: red;\">顯示肖在一群女性保鏢陪同下被帶走。</span>報道指不清楚肖在房間內發生什麼事，但在酒店的走廊是沒有發生爭執。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033e37f3c98cb5d4c88a43230cabe99b62131a22","tid":102432,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823083d4d2c5ba04597ed174810cae726f77f22e","tid":102432,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"ifc保安起碼識報警，女保標負責做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d2c29bdfc43bb5f0dd1d6da2dfa36baa9dbef2","tid":102432,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ifc保安起碼識報警，女保標負責做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保護細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4b2d110bba195aee0451fca819555d9b0e1162","tid":102432,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ifc保安起碼識報警，女保標負責做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保護細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n扑"},{"pid":"f0b2e973bc0531056cee6ad47947eee07274eb79","tid":102432,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ifc保安起碼識報警，